    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Shannon, 325 is the correct temperature, and as long as your oven is running accurately, 25 minutes should be just about right.  Maybe try setting the timer for 20 minutes, though, and checking them then.  Mine are usually perfect at 25 minutes, but you might like yours a shade lighter.</p>
