  <li id="comment-17078" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2010/05/her-recipe-box/#comment-17078"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-01-04T19:03:55-05:00">Saturday, January 4, 2014 at 7:03 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I just found this recipe after trying to find a recipe that might appeal to my  teenager to eat breakfast before school, because she won&#39;t eat anything. It&#39;s her last year of school, she needs brain food for the forthcoming exams. Sorted! she loves them. Only problem is there nae enough sugar and cinnamon for 6 slices of bread but then maybe loaves in Scotland are much bigger than the American counterparts! For a good wee warburtons loaf, increase by half again!</p>
    </div>

